          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-drew" title="Mr David Drew">Mr. Drew</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            To be fair to the processors&#x2014;I have the biggest dairy in my constituency&#x2014;there has been a huge reduction in capacity. That has come at a cost. One thing that I said earlier, which was slightly misconstrued, was that we need to rebuild the relationship between the processors and the producers. That can be done only if the processing industry is reasonably efficient.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-03533'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031028_WH_95'>  </a>
